-- UBI CEO, speaking about probe, says confident things will be sorted out
-- By Silvia Aloisi
-- Wed May 14, 2014 09:21AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, May 14 (Reuters) - The chief executive of UBI Banca <UBI.MI>, Italy's fifth-biggest lender, said on Wednesday he was confident the a probe into the bank's top management and its leasing unit could be successfully dealt with.

